  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695310/extras/d795e046361ffafd4429e99a50de4583.avif?t=1629266794\" width=550 height=108 /></span><br><br>In Pro Pain Labs you play as an acrobatic robot named S.A.M or 'Super Awesome Machine' designed to navigate weird and unusual environments filled with deadly spikes, saws, and lasers. <br><br>Test your skills by conquering various levels each with its own unique design. You can collect vials throughout the game to unlock special challenge levels designed to be brutal and unforgiving. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695310/extras/56c518f0c1b7d6502837c90874315c45.poster.avif?t=1629266794\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695310/extras/56c518f0c1b7d6502837c90874315c45.webm?t=1629266794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695310/extras/56c518f0c1b7d6502837c90874315c45.mp4?t=1629266794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 51 Handcrafted Levels<br></li><li> Collectable Vials<br></li><li> Lots of Traps<br></li><li> Steam Achievements<br></li><li> Steam Cloud</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695310/extras/d795e046361ffafd4429e99a50de4583.avif?t=1629266794\" width=550 height=108 /></span><br><br>In Pro Pain Labs you play as an acrobatic robot named S.A.M or 'Super Awesome Machine' designed to navigate weird and unusual environments filled with deadly spikes, saws, and lasers. <br><br>Test your skills by conquering various levels each with its own unique design. You can collect vials throughout the game to unlock special challenge levels designed to be brutal and unforgiving. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695310/extras/56c518f0c1b7d6502837c90874315c45.poster.avif?t=1629266794\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695310/extras/56c518f0c1b7d6502837c90874315c45.webm?t=1629266794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695310/extras/56c518f0c1b7d6502837c90874315c45.mp4?t=1629266794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 51 Handcrafted Levels<br></li><li> Collectable Vials<br></li><li> Lots of Traps<br></li><li> Steam Achievements<br></li><li> Steam Cloud</li></ul>",
